'''贝克斯菲尔德'''（{{lang en|'''Bakersfield'''}}），美国华裔又稱'''北架斐''','''碧克斐''','''碧克菲''',或'''貝克菲尔'''位于[[美国|美国]][[加利福尼亚州|加利福尼亚州]]中南部，是[[克恩县|克恩县]]的县治所在。{{GR|6}}根據[[美國2010年人口普查|2010年人口普查]]，本城共有人口347,483人。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://factfinder2.census.gov/ |title=2010 census factfinder2 |accessdate=2013-07-30 |archive-date=2013-09-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130911234518/http://factfinder2.census.gov/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>[http://www.dof.ca.gov/research/demographic/state_census_data_center/census_2010/documents/2010Census_Pop_Rankers.xls Top Population Rank: Cities 2000 and 2010] {{Wayback|url=http://www.dof.ca.gov/research/demographic/state_census_data_center/census_2010/documents/2010Census_Pop_Rankers.xls |date=20110721033303 }}. California Department of Finance. Retrieved March 14, 2012.</ref>本城於1869年成立<ref name=Historic>{{Cite book |author=Mildred Brooke Hoover, Douglas E. Kyle |title=Historic Spots in California |publisher=[[史丹福大學出版社|Stanford University Press]] |isbn=978-0-8047-1734-2 |year=1990 |url=http://books.google.com/books?id=p2WrAAAAIAAJ&printsec=frontcover&lr=&source=gbs_book_other_versions_r&cad=1_1#PPA128,M1 |page=128 |access-date=2013-07-30 |archive-date=2013-10-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131013033539/http://books.google.com/books?id=p2WrAAAAIAAJ&printsec=frontcover&lr=&source=gbs_book_other_versions_r&cad=1_1#PPA128,M1 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.bakersfieldmagazine.net/arts/kern-history/456-kern-county-shapers |title=Kern County Shapers |publisher=Bakersfield Magazine |first=Gordon F. |last=Lull |accessdate=2013-01-17 |quote=Baker ...was admitted to the Ohio bar at age 19 and later appointed a colonel in his home state's militia. |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121230192356/http://www.bakersfieldmagazine.net/arts/kern-history/456-kern-county-shapers |archivedate=2012-12-30 }}</ref>，是美國第二大不直接連接到一條[[州際公路|州際公路]]的城市。<ref>[http://www.bakersfieldchamber.org/images/documents/8137_3659.PDF Community Profile] {{Wayback|url=http://www.bakersfieldchamber.org/images/documents/8137_3659.PDF |date=20140630071628 }}. Greater Bakersfield Chamber of Commerce. Page 4. Retrieved March 14, 2012.</ref>農業、石油、加工和製造業是城市主要的經濟。<ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.archive.org/stream/up5californiawater20178calirich/up5californiawater20178calirich_djvu.txt |title=Full text of "California water"|work=CONTROLLING THE KERN RIVER Problems|publisher= archive.org| accessdate=2009-04-07}}</ref>贝克斯菲尔德是加州第9大城市，美國第51大城市。

==地理==
根據[[美國2000年人口普查|2000年人口普查]]，本城面積為{{convert|143.6|sqmi|sqkm|2}}，其中{{convert|142.2|sqmi|sqkm|2}}為陸地，{{convert|1.4|sqmi|sqkm|2}}為水域。<ref name ="Gazetteer files">{{cite web|title=US Gazetteer files 2010|url=http://www.census.gov/geo/www/gazetteer/files/Gaz_places_national.txt|publisher=[[美国人口调查局|United States Census Bureau]]|accessdate=2013-01-25|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/699nOulzi?url=http://www.census.gov/geo/www/gazetteer/files/Gaz_places_national.txt|archive-date=2012-07-14|dead-url=yes}}</ref>本城延伸至[[紅杉國家森林|紅杉國家森林]]。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.bakersfieldhelpwanted.org/ |title=Bakersfield Geography |work=source |accessdate=2010 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101011234406/http://www.bakersfieldhelpwanted.org/ |archivedate=2010年10月11日 |deadurl=yes }}</ref> 

===氣候===
贝克斯菲尔德擁有[[沙漠氣候|沙漠氣候]]<ref>Peel, M. C., Finlayson, B. L., and McMahon, T. A.: {{tsl|en|Media:Americas Köppen Map original colors.png||Updated world map of the Köppen-Geiger climate classification}}, Hydrol. Earth Syst. Sci., 11, 1633–1644, 200 7.</ref>，其夏季漫長、炎熱、乾燥，冬季短促、涼爽、濕潤。贝克斯菲尔德是美國晴天最多的城市之一。<ref>Ozborn, Liz. [http://www.currentresults.com/Weather-Extremes/US/sunniest.php Sunniest Places in United States] {{Wayback|url=http://www.currentresults.com/Weather-Extremes/US/sunniest.php |date=20130802073530 }}. Current Results. Retrieved March 13, 2012.</ref>该市平均每20至30年才下一次雪。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.sjgs.com/bakersfield.html |title=Bakersfield Climate |work=San Joaquin Geological Society |accessdate=2010-09-25 |archive-date=2011-07-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110716080542/http://www.sjgs.com/bakersfield.html |dead-url=no
}}</ref>上一场可测量的降雪为1999年1月25日。<ref>{{cite web  |url=http://ggweather.com  |title=Golden Gate Weather Services  |publisher=GGWeather.com  |accessdate=2008-11-29  |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081219224844/http://ggweather.com/  |archivedate=2008-12-19  |deadurl=no 
 }}</ref><ref name = "NWS Hanford, CA"/>降雨量最高的一個月是2010年12月，其降雨量為{{convert|5.82|in|mm|disp=flip}}。<ref>{{cite web|title=Bakersfield Monthly Rainfall By Year|url=http://www.wrh.noaa.gov/hnx/bfl/normals/bflrnyr.pdf|publisher=National Weather Service|accessdate=2011-07-03|archive-date=2014-07-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140717231340/http://www.wrh.noaa.gov/hnx/bfl/normals/bflrnyr.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>而降雨量最高的一天是1978年2月9日，其降雨量為{{convert|2.29|in|mm|disp=flip}}。<ref name = "NWS Hanford, CA"/>

根据1991至2020年在佛雷斯诺优胜美地国际机场的数据，日最低气温低于或等于{{convert|0|C}}的平均日数为9.9天；日最高气温达{{convert|30|C}}的日数年均有138天，{{convert|40|C}}以上的有12天。<ref name = "NWS Hanford, CA"/>最冷月（12月、1月）均温{{convert|49.2|F|1|disp=flip}}，极端最低气温{{convert|13|F|0|disp=flip}}（1905年12月24日）。<ref name = "NWS Hanford, CA"/>最热月（7月）均温{{convert|84.8|F|1|disp=flip}}，极端最高气温{{convert|118|F|0|disp=flip}}（1908年7月28日）。<ref name = "NWS Hanford, CA"/>年均降水量约{{convert|6.36|in|mm|disp=flip}}，年极端最少降水量为{{convert|1.87|in|mm|disp=flip}}（1959年），最多为{{convert|13.32|in|mm|disp=flip}}（1998年）；12月至3月占全年大约72%的降水量。<ref name = "NWS Hanford, CA"/>无霜期平均有324天（1月24日至12月14日）。<ref name = "NWS Hanford, CA"/>

